<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.9.9">
<l>piṟaiyuṭai vāṇutal piṉṉaiti ṟattumuṉ ṉēyoru kālceru villurumiṉ</l>
<l>maṟaiyuṭai mālviṭai yēḻaṭart tāṟkiṭan tāṉtaṭañ cūḻntaḻa kāyakacci</l>
<l>kaṟaiyuṭai vāḷmaṟa maṉṉarke ṭakkaṭal pōlamu ḻaṅkuṅku ralkaṭuvāy</l>
<l>paṟaiyuṭaip pallavar kōṉpaṇin tapara mēccura viṇṇaka ramatuvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In fair Kacci encircled by ponds, the very place for him</l>
<l rend="indent">who once previously in battle</l>
<l>Destroyed seven thunderous, great bulls with spots because of Piṉṉai,</l>
<l rend="indent">her forehead with the glow of a crescent,</l>
<l>Is Paramēccura Viṇṇakaram where bowed the king of the Pallavas</l>
<l rend="indent">with a cruel-mouthed drum</l>
<l>Whose voice roars like the sea so that brave kings with bloodied swords perish.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
